{"tid":2514561,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Konami 宣布退出 2021 年 E3 展 強調正在開發數個重要專案","createTime":"2021-05-03T10:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T10:45:40.000Z","uid":14812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f75b0a988087e58a01062124504a97f157b37227","tid":2514561,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"Konami 於官方推特宣布，將退出 2021 年的 E3 展，並表示由於時間的關係，還沒準備好在這次的 E3 展示。但也請粉絲放心，目前正在開發數個重要的專案，請粉絲們期待後續幾個月的消息；也表達支持今年的 E3 展，祝福參與的廠商。<br />\n<br />\nKonami 原先是主辦單位 ESA 最先公開參加的廠商之一，第一波名單包含任天堂、Capcom 等 8 家廠商。<br />\n <br />\n　　根據外國媒體 VGC 的報導，原本 Konami 的經營者拒絕將遊戲授權給其他廠商開發，但《潛龍諜影 求生戰（Metal Gear Survive）》及《魂斗羅 RC 聯盟》的失敗，可能讓公司的想法轉變，傾向於授權製作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=5137116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D5137116&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=9de35b00\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=5137116</a>"},{"pid":"ad51f287b8cb397734ca175db4a52b81a9c3a818","tid":2514561,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"手機game公司 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8320f58aba51e511095dc597cc4fdd3d90ef6f57","tid":2514561,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾game公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb534ad1b06d164ae380425970a5cefbf4010473","tid":2514561,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"Metal Gear M<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"